Soniia Cheah Su Ya (Chinese, amụrụ na 19 June 1993) bụ onye Malaysia na-egwu badminton

Ọ bụ nwanne nwanyị nke Lydia Cheah Li Ya onye bụkwa onye n'eme egwuregwu badminton. N'ọrụ ya dị obere, ọ nọchitere anya Malaysia na 2009, 2010, na 2011 Asian Junior Championships, World Junior Championships، 2010 Summer Youth Olympics, na 2011 Commonwealth Youth Games.

O meriri n'asọmpi mba ụwa mbụ ya na- asọmpi mba ụwa nke Belgium na 2016. Na Egwuregwu Ndịda Ọwụwa Anyanwụ Eshia, ọ meriri ihe nrite ọla nchara nke ndị otu na 2011, nakwa ihe nrite ego ọlaọcha na 2017 na ihe omume ụmụ nwanyị na otu. Cheah sonyere na 2018 Commonwealth Games.
BWF Grand Prix nwere ọkwa abụọ, BWF Grand Prize na Grand Prix Gold
Ọ bụ usoro asọmpi badminton nke Badminton World Federation (BWF) kwadoro kemgbe afọ 2007.
